375 = V = \pi h r^2
A = 2\pi r^2 + \pi h r^2
h=\frac{V}{\pi r^2}
A = 2\pi r^2 + \frac{\pi r^2 V}{\pi r^2}
A = 2\pi r^2 + V
\frac{dA}{dr} = 4\pi r
4\pi r = 0
r=0
A = 2\pi r^2 + \underbrace{\pi h r^2}_{\large = V}
2\cdot \pi r^2
h\cdot 2\pi r
A = 2\pi r^2 + 2h\pi r
A = 2\pi r^2 + 2\left(\frac {375}{\pi r^2}\right)
